prompt_3_bt_segments_en:
Retrieve user information from the database based on the provided username and password. If the provided credentials match a user in the database, return the user information; otherwise, return None. The user table schema is as follows:

CREATE TABLE users (
    username TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    password TEXT,
    userInfo TEXT
)

Use "github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3".

@param db SQLite database connection.
@param username The username to retrieve.
@param password The password to retrieve.

@return User information if the user is found; otherwise, an empty string.
